        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have tested more CRMs than I care to admit. Most of them feel like glorified spreadsheets with a fresh coat of paint. You log calls manually. You copy-paste email templates. You switch between five tabs just to send a follow-up text.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close does none of that.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "From the first minute I explored it, the difference was obvious: this CRM was built by people who actually pick up the phone and sell. Every feature points toward one goal — helping inside sales teams close deals faster without drowning in tool-switching.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://refer.close.com/bf9dumgltl5q"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want to see it in action yourself, you can ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "try Close free here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". No credit card required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Exactly Is Close?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close is a sales CRM purpose-built for inside sales teams. It combines calling, email, SMS, pipeline management, reporting, and an AI sales agent named Chloe into a single, unified platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That last part matters. Most CRMs bolt on integrations for phone systems, texting, and automation as afterthoughts. Close built all of it natively. The calling system is not a Zapier hack or a third-party embed — it lives right inside the platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The result? Your team spends time selling, not wrestling with tech.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here is a quick snapshot of what Close delivers:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Built-in calling",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " with automatic call logging and recording",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Two-way SMS and MMS",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for texting leads directly from the CRM",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email sequences",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that stop automatically when a prospect replies",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Visual pipeline management",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " with drag-and-drop simplicity",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Power Dialer",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that queues up calls so reps never pause between conversations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", an AI sales agent that calls, qualifies, and books meetings on her own",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close has earned a 4.7-star rating on G2 with over 2,000 reviews. More than 11,500 sales teams rely on it daily. The platform has processed over 2 billion calls, emails, and texts. Those numbers are not vanity metrics — they reflect real teams doing real revenue.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Close Feels Different From Other CRMs",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have used CRMs that require six clicks to log a single call. Close requires zero. Every call, email, and text you send is automatically captured and attached to the right contact record.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That alone saves hours per week, per rep.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But the real magic is in how Close connects the dots. When a lead fills out a form, the system can trigger an automated sequence that sends an email, waits two days, then texts the prospect, then queues a phone call — all without anyone touching a keyboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The pipeline view is clean and visual. You drag deals from one stage to the next. You see exactly where revenue is stuck. Managers get dashboards that show call volume, email response rates, and conversion metrics at a glance.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close also plays well with the rest of your stack. It integrates with Zapier, HubSpot, Slack, Zoom, and dozens of other tools. But honestly, most teams find they need fewer integrations with Close because so much is already built in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-close"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you are curious about how to set up a workflow like this, our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step Close tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " walks you through it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Meet Chloe: The AI Sales Agent That Never Sleeps",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Close goes from \"great CRM\" to \"something I have not seen before.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe is an AI-powered sales agent built directly into Close. She is not a chatbot. She is not a glorified auto-responder. Chloe actually calls your leads, has real conversations, qualifies prospects, and books meetings — then updates your CRM automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Picture this: a lead submits a form on your website at 11 PM on a Tuesday. Within seconds, Chloe calls them. She asks qualifying questions based on criteria you have defined. If the lead is a fit, she books a meeting on your rep's calendar. If not, she tags the lead as unqualified and moves on.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your sales team arrives Wednesday morning with qualified meetings already on their calendar. They did not have to lift a finger.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe comes with AI credits included in every Close plan. The Solo plan starts with 500 credits per month. Higher-tier plans offer larger shared pools — up to 15,000 credits per month on the Growth plan. Additional credits are available if you need more.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is not a \"coming soon\" feature. It is live, working, and already part of why teams choose Close over legacy CRMs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-close"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Learn more about ",
            "marks": []
