        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced AI Credits System",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Every plan now includes a monthly pool of AI credits that powers Chloe and other AI features. The Growth plan offers a shared pool of 1,500 credits per user, capped at 15,000 per month across your team. Credits refresh monthly.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smarter Sequences",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Close has refined its email and SMS sequences to be even more behavior-driven. Sequences now pause automatically not just on replies but on specific reply sentiment, so a \"not interested\" email does not get treated the same as a \"tell me more.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Power Dialer Upgrades",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — The Power Dialer now supports local presence dialing, which means your outbound calls show a local area code. Answer rates go up. Conversations happen more often.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pipeline Forecasting",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Managers can now see weighted pipeline forecasts that factor in deal velocity, historical close rates, and rep performance. No more guessing what this quarter will look like.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Improved Reporting Dashboard",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — The reporting suite got a visual overhaul. You can build custom reports with drag-and-drop widgets, schedule automated report delivery to Slack or email, and compare performance across time periods with a single click.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/close-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Check out all the ",
