      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Close Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close is not trying to be everything to everyone. It is laser-focused on inside sales teams — people who sell primarily through phone, email, and SMS rather than in-person meetings.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here is who gets the most value out of Close:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small to mid-size sales teams (2–100 reps)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Close scales beautifully. The Essentials plan is perfect for a team of five. The Growth plan handles teams of fifty without blinking. You add users and the system just works.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaaS companies selling B2B",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — If your sales cycle involves demos, follow-ups, and multi-touch outreach, Close was practically designed for you. The automation sequences alone can replace an entire outbound stack.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies and service businesses",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Teams that need to manage hundreds of leads in different pipeline stages will appreciate the visual pipeline and automatic activity logging.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Solo founders doing their own sales",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — The Solo plan at $9/month (billed annually) gives you a full CRM with calling, SMS, email, and 500 AI credits. That is more firepower than most enterprise tools offer at ten times the price.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Teams replacing multiple tools",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — If you currently use a CRM, a separate dialer, an email sequencing tool, and a texting platform, Close consolidates all of that into one login and one bill.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
