        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At the Growth tier, you unlock the full power of automation, advanced reporting, and a substantial AI credit pool. For teams doing serious outbound volume, this is where Close becomes a revenue engine.",
