        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is Close CRM and who is it for?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close is a sales CRM built specifically for inside sales teams. It combines calling, email, SMS, pipeline management, and an AI sales agent named Chloe into one platform. It is ideal for B2B SaaS companies, agencies, and small-to-mid-size teams (2–100 reps) who sell primarily through phone, email, and text rather than in-person meetings.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Chloe, the AI sales agent in Close, work?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Chloe is an AI agent built directly into Close CRM. She automatically calls new leads the moment they come in, has real conversations to qualify prospects based on your criteria, and books meetings on your team's calendar. She updates the CRM automatically so your reps arrive each morning with qualified meetings already scheduled.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Close CRM cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close starts at $9 per user per month (billed annually) on the Solo plan, which includes calling, SMS, email, and 500 AI credits. The Essentials plan is $35/user/month and the Growth plan is $99/user/month with more automation and AI credits. All plans come with a 14-day free trial and no credit card is required to start.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
